285
00:15:47,105 --> 00:15:48,146
Yes.

286
00:15:59,575 --> 00:16:05,349
♪Like petals fall, gone with the clouds♪

287
00:16:05,350 --> 00:16:11,345
♪Like stars fade fast in open skies♪

288
00:16:11,462 --> 00:16:17,161
♪Like snowflakes melting softly
in the evening haze♪

289
00:16:17,162 --> 00:16:23,486
♪Like your fleeting glance
