292
00:16:35,437 --> 00:16:41,161
♪Like fleeting thoughts
that surge and then unwind♪

293
00:16:41,162 --> 00:16:47,099
♪Chance meetings fade,
just empty rooms left behind♪

294
00:16:47,100 --> 00:16:52,732
♪You brought a wave
that stirred a wild, restless sea♪

295
00:16:53,012 --> 00:16:58,907
♪Light as a feather,
yet it sank an island deep in me♪

296
00:16:59,087 --> 00:17:05,645
♪In that one moment,
